  "name": "Punitive Transformation",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/spells/light-royal-1.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can transform an opponent into a harmless animal as if using @Compendium[pf1.spells.t8ei2mrmqg7252vw]{Baleful Polymorph}. This transformation lasts 1 round per oracle level. Transforming another creature causes the first to immediately revert to normal.</p>\n<p>You may use this ability a number of times per day equal to your Charisma modifier.</p>\n<p>You must be at least 7th level before selecting this revelation.</p>"
